l-home" class="sc-2a82f923-0 woSiQ"><div class="sc-2a82f923-1 ccDloO"><a href="/editorials"><h2 class="sc-2a82f923-2 hEjAWI">Artículos</h2></a></div><a href="/editorials" class="sc-2a82f923-4 ccYAuL">Más</a></div><div class="sc-a418fb23-1 jjOJwB"> </div><div page="editorial-home" class="sc-a418fb23-0 hsvnei"><div page="editorial-home" class="sc-4a7d729f-1 irhQms"><div class="sc-4a7d729f-0 jHqsbK"><div class="sc-4a7d729f-9"><img alt="the-clans-battle-in-the-north - editorial" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F9%2F5%2F8%2F958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/></div><div class="sc-4a7d729f-7 ikJonP">Events</div></div><div class="sc-4a7d729f-2 lcNRbt"><a href="https://en.aptoide.com/editorial/the-clans-battle-in-the-north" class="sc-4a7d729f-4 fdqrnU">The Clans Battle in the North</a><div class="sc-4a7d729f-8 hXeUkR"><span type="description" class="sc-4a7d729f-3 iXPmSu">The Clans Battle in the North competition is now live, giving players the chance to bring glory to their Clan and Kingdom. Running from July 15, 2026, to August 1, 2026, this global event challenges players to work together, complete objectives, and climb the rankings.

Throughout the event, you’ll battle rival players, gather valuable resources, train powerful warriors, and complete a variety of tasks to earn points for your Clan. Every contribution helps strengthen your Kingdom and brings your Clan closer to victory.

Whether you’re a seasoned warrior or a rising Jarl, teamwork and strategy will be the key to success. Join forces with your clanmates, complete the event objectives, and compete for honor during this limited-time competition.

Prepare your army, rally your Clan, and make your Kingdom famous before The Clans Battle in the North ends on August 1, 2026.</span></div></div></div><div page="editorial-home" class="sc-4a7d729f-1 irhQms"><div class="sc-4a7d729f-0 jHqsbK"><div class="sc-4a7d729f-9"><img alt="wartune-ultra-dinah-s-carnival - editorial" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" src="https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2F7%2F3%2F2%2F732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75"/></div><div class="sc-4a7d729f-7 ikJonP">Events</div></div><div class="sc-4a7d729f-2 lcNRbt"><a href="https://en.aptoide.com/editorial/wartune-ultra-dinah-s-carnival" class="sc-4a7d729f-4 fdqrnU">Wartune Ultra: Dinah’s Carnival</a><div class="sc-4a7d729f-8 hXeUkR"><span type="description" class="sc-4a7d729f-3 iXPmSu">Dinah’s Birthday Carnival has arrived in Wartune Ultra, bringing a festive event packed with exclusive cosmetics, special activities, and exciting rewards. From July 12, 2026, to August 7, 2026, players can join the celebration and unlock a variety of limited-time content.

Earn the elegant Starway Mirror Fashion, ride the majestic Star Shadow Dragon Mount, and, on Legacy servers, collect the vibrant Colorful Wonderland recolor collection. Light birthday candles to obtain rare items, exclusive appearances, and special event merchandise.

Complete Daily Quests to earn free draws, and team up with other players to collect Blessing Points and unlock milestone rewards. Every challenge completed brings you one step closer to even more valuable prizes.

Join the celebration before August 7, 2026, and don’t miss your chance to collect these exclusive Carnival rewards while they’re available.</span></div></div></div><div page="editorial-home" class="sc-4a7d729f-1 irhQms"><div class="sc-4a7d729f-0 jHqsbK"><div class="sc-4a7d729f-9"><img alt="usa-only-get-a-free-4-99-coin-pack - editorial" loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-nimg="fill" style="position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;object-fit:cover;color:transparent" sizes="100vw" srcSet="https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, https://static-images.aptoide.com/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.aptoide.com%2Fimgs%2Ff%2Fa%2Ff%2Ffaf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png%3Fw%3D374%26h%3D198&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w" sr