, complete the event objectives, and compete for honor during this limited-time competition.\n\nPrepare your army, rally your Clan, and make your Kingdom famous before The Clans Battle in the North ends on August 1, 2026.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/9/5/8/958523bab6ab862d5fc36000b3d83486.jpg","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=817/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-07-17 11:23:55","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"816","title":"Wartune Ultra: Dinah’s Carnival","slug":"wartune-ultra-dinah-s-carnival","message":"Events","summary":"Dinah’s Birthday Carnival has arrived in Wartune Ultra, bringing a festive event packed with exclusive cosmetics, special activities, and exciting rewards. From July 12, 2026, to August 7, 2026, players can join the celebration and unlock a variety of limited-time content.\n\nEarn the elegant Starway Mirror Fashion, ride the majestic Star Shadow Dragon Mount, and, on Legacy servers, collect the vibrant Colorful Wonderland recolor collection. Light birthday candles to obtain rare items, exclusive appearances, and special event merchandise.\n\nComplete Daily Quests to earn free draws, and team up with other players to collect Blessing Points and unlock milestone rewards. Every challenge completed brings you one step closer to even more valuable prizes.\n\nJoin the celebration before August 7, 2026, and don’t miss your chance to collect these exclusive Carnival rewards while they’re available.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/7/3/2/732666033b6e4dade775dd51a6b64b06.jpg","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=816/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-07-17 11:08:43","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"814","title":"USA Only - Get a Free $4.99 Coin Pack","slug":"usa-only-get-a-free-4-99-coin-pack","message":"Events","summary":"Ready to kick-start your Cash Club Casino adventure? New players in the United States can now claim a FREE $4.99 Coin Pack with their first in-game purchase through Aptoide.\n\nThis limited-time promotion is available to eligible players in the U.S. who have never made a purchase in Cash Club Casino through Aptoide. Simply select the $4.99 Coin Pack, complete your first purchase, and Aptoide will cover the cost.\n\nIt’s the perfect way to boost your balance, enjoy more spins, and get extra value from your gameplay right from the start.\n\nThis exclusive offer is available only to eligible players in the United States. Promotional rewards are available while supplies last and may be subject to redemption limits, so be sure to claim your reward before the offer ends.\n\nDon’t miss your chance to get a FREE $4.99 Coin Pack and start spinning with an extra boost today!","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/f/a/f/faf63bb5c6f92a68d3ff3f29e954e53b.png","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=814/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-07-10 11:02:25","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"812","title":"Legacy of Discord-FuriousWings","slug":"legacy-of-discord-furiouswings","message":"Game of the Week","summary":"Legacy of Discord-FuriousWings is a mobile action MMORPG built around real-time combat, flashy skills, and character progression. It suits Android players who want quick dungeon runs, competitive arenas, and a dark fantasy style.\n\nIf you searched for a Legacy of Discord-FuriousWings review, the short answer is simple. This is a combat-first RPG where movement, upgrades, wings, and PvP pressure define the experience.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/2/e/7/2e7440a8d6154c3a05e611a44c86296a.png","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=812/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-07-10 10:46:05","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"810","title":"Duck Survival - Frozen Expedition","slug":"duck-survival-frozen-expedition","message":"Events","summary":"The Duck Survival – Frozen Expedition event is coming soon, bringing an all-new guild adventure packed with battles, exploration, and valuable rewards. The event runs from July 3, 2026, to July 14, 2026, with the Frozen Expedition gameplay beginning on July 6 for eligible players.\n\nAvailable to servers that have been open for at least 15 days and players who have cleared Stage 20, the Frozen Expedition introduces powerful new Gene Tech abilities. Team up with your guild to defeat monsters, compete in the Gladiator Arena, capture cities, and earn abundant rewards and resources while fighting for your guild’s glory.\n\nThe Expedition season lasts for four weeks, ending on August 2, followed by a Truce period from August 3 to August 9 before the next Expedition begins.\n\nGather your guild, prepare for the Frozen Expedition, and conquer the battlefield to earn exclusive rewards.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/b/2/4/b24b212386fe728f9b7028f2054240e4.png","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=810/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-07-10 10:44:53","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"807","title":"Vikings: War of Clans","slug":"vikings-war-of-clans","message":"New Games","summary":"Vikings: War of Clans Is Now Available on Aptoide – Claim an Exclusive Starter Pack!","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/9/b/1/9b16802063b5a488ed6836c901709c31.png","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=807/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-07-03 16:31:01","flair":null},{"card_id":"806","title":"Kickoff Football 26: Be A Pro","slug":"kickoff-football-26-be-a-pro","message":"Game of the Week","summary":"If you searched for Kickoff Football 26: Be A Pro, you likely want a fast answer. This Android football game focuses on living the rise of a player, not only winning matches.\n\nKickoff Football 26: Be A Pro is an Android football game built around player career progression, match performance, and pro-style decision making. It suits fans who want short football sessions with a personal journey at the center.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/f/e/d/fed95147de1e6b6b81f775279e1f08da.png","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=806/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-07-03 16:27:52","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"802","title":"New Slot Beam Them All","slug":"new-slot-beam-them-all","message":"Events","summary":"The New Slot Beam Them All update is here, bringing a fun extraterrestrial adventure filled with farm animals, exciting bonus features, and rewarding gameplay. The event runs from June 18, 2026, to July 2, 2026.\n\nHelp a UFO collect adorable farm animals—including cows, sheep, and pigs—as you spin through this colorful slot adventure. Activate three special game features, trigger powerful bonus modes, and chase huge multipliers while working toward massive jackpots.\n\nWith charming visuals, entertaining sound effects, and exciting rewards, New Slot Beam Them All offers a fresh slot experience packed with surprises. Every spin brings you one step closer to bigger wins.\n\nJoin the event, activate the bonus features, and beam up your rewards before July 2, 2026.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/8/0/1/801c3a8f345ff0ae68d8f1693c3c3f78.jpg","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=802/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-06-26 10:58:43","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"801","title":"Unidentified Signals","slug":"unidentified-signals","message":"Events","summary":"The Unidentified Signals event is now live, introducing the legendary Tailsting mech and the powerful new Versa heavy weapon. Running from June 16, 2026, to July 3, 2026, this limited-time event gives players new ways to expand their arsenal and earn exclusive rewards.\n\nDuring the event, players can test Tailsting in Onslaught Trial mode, complete special event activities, and unlock a variety of rewards, including exclusive skins, implants, and pilot loyalty program rewards. The new Versa weapon also features two firing modes, offering greater flexibility in both close-range and long-range combat.\n\nJoin the Unidentified Signals event, master the new mech and weapon, and claim your exclusive rewards before the event ends on July 3, 2026.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/3/c/2/3c22077871c07f0f248404cbf5eb6426.png","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=801/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-06-26 10:53:49","flair":"appc-bonus-25"},{"card_id":"794","title":"Ludus - Clan War","slug":"ludus-clan-war","message":"Special Event","summary":"The Clan War event is now live, giving players the chance to battle rival clans and compete for a place on the Global Rankings. The competition runs from June 17, 2026, to June 21, 2026.","icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/8/9/2/89207b49687716306b246b08e537933e.jpg","url":"https://ws75.aptoide.com/api/7/user/action/item/card/get/id=794/store_name=aptoide-web","views":0,"date":"2026-06-19 12:49:50","flair":null}],"next":12,"offset":0,"count":10,"total":382},"editorsChoice":{"title":"Editors Choice","list":[{"id":75033048,"icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/b/e/a/bea00597d20ae7479d6fdac22e23340b_icon.png","name":"Illusion Connect: Re","score":4.8,"size":"825.5 MB","store":"catappult","uname":"illusion-connect-re","trusted":false,"downloads":0,"parsedName":"Illusion Connect: Re","graphic":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/4/6/2/462a3a0993e395b320fed02c1a48e7fc_fgraphic.jpg","package":"com.sugargame.mjlj.aptoide","appcoins":true,"filePath":"","malwareRank":"","isOfficialApp":true},{"id":75723159,"icon":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/f/e/d/fed95147de1e6b6b81f775279e1f08da_icon.png","name":"Kickoff Football 26: Be A Pro","score":5,"size":"939 MB","store":"catappult","uname":"kickoff-football-2026","trusted":false,"downloads":100000,"parsedName":"Kickoff Football 26: Be A Pro","graphic":"https://cdn.aptoide.com/imgs/c/a/f/caf1e4685bfc63e7a00661a6a094ae43_fgraphic.jpg","package":"